nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE A LITTLE STRONGER WHILE MOVING QUICKLY NORTHWESTWARD WELL NORTH OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS...
summary: ...HENRIETTE A LITTLE STRONGER WHILE MOVING QUICKLY NORTHWESTWARD WELL NORTH OF THE HAWAIIAN ISLANDS... As of 5:00 AM HST Mon Aug 11 the center of Henriette was located near 28.8, -156.5 with movement NW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 986 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 85 mph.
